parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Climate Control and Audio System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the climate control and audio system can cause the defroster to malfunction, leading to reduced visibility and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The climate control and audio system fail to function
the defroster does not work
the radio does not turn on
and the air conditioning and heating controls are inoperable.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Crankshaft and Camshaft Position Sensor Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the crankshaft and camshaft position sensors can cause the engine to stall, leading to loss of power and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The engine stalls
the check engine light comes on
and the vehicle may experience difficulty starting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the electrical system can cause various safety features to fail, including the horn, lights, and brakes, leading to increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The horn honks continuously
the lights malfunction
and the brakes may fail to function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to loss of power and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The ignition switch fails to return to the "on" position
making it difficult to start the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Vehicle Seat and Restraint System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the vehicle seat and restraint system can cause the seat to move unexpectedly, leading to loss of control and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The seat moves forward or backward unexpectedly
and the airbag light may come on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the crank/cam position sensor can cause the engine to stall, resulting in a loss of power steering and brakes, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls without warning
the check engine light illuminates
the service engine soon light illuminates
the VDC off light illuminates
the slip light illuminates
the vehicle loses power
and the vehicle is difficult to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive oil consumption can lead to engine failure, which can cause accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle consumes excessive amounts of oil
the oil warning light illuminates
and the engine may stall or fail to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failure can cause the vehicle to stall, resulting in a loss of power steering and brakes, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The radio and temperature control malfunction
the fan comes on high and switches to air conditioning
and the vehicle stalls.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature brake wear and failure can lead to reduced stopping power, increased risk of accidents, and potential harm to occupants and other road users.
symptoms: Squealing or grinding noise when applying brakes
excessive brake dust
brake pedal vibration
and reduced braking performance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake system failure can cause loss of control, accidents, and potential harm to occupants and other road users.
symptoms: Brake pedal goes to the floor
brake failure warning lights illuminate
and loss of braking performance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Excessive brake noise and vibration can be a sign of impending brake failure, which can lead to accidents and potential harm to occupants and other road users.
symptoms: Squealing
grinding
or vibrating noise when applying brakes
and excessive brake dust.
